					<![CDATA[
						 <p>We don't know how or why the statues are appearing, or what happens to the people afterwards, if anything. Better not to keep feeding the thing we don't fully understand if we can avoid it. As for the fence-cutting, it's better to outline everything clearly to avoid any issues. Better safe than sorry.</p> 
